  "wpt_descr": "Adding WPT not feasible for this change. Unit tests have been added for automated testing for the feature. A manual WPT has been created for the change.\n\nLink - https://wpt.live/html/editing/editing-0/autocorrection/autocorrect-off-touch-keyboard-manual.html",
  "webview_risks": "No. This change is Windows-only. It has no impact on Android, Android WebView, or any non-Windows platform. A kill switch (kTSFHonorAutocorrectOff) is in place regardless.",
